USA: CCC seeks 33,000 T U.S. white wheat for Bangladesh.CCC seeks 33,000 T U.S. white wheat for Bangladesh.The Commodity Credit Corp said on Tuesday it is seeking up to 33,000 tonnes of U.S. No.2 soft white wheat for donation to Bangladesh.The shipment period is slated for September 10-October 5.The CCC, which is part os the U.S. Department of Agriculture, said the wheat must be tested for vomitoxin with a maximum level of two parts per million.The wheat must also originate in U.S. locations where Karnal Bunt (Tilletia Indica) is not known to occur.Offers are due on August 27, it said.--Doris Frankel 312-983-7305